{"tid":2089957,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"收口抄家治國平天下 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-07-02T02:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T02:09:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"322c00b1c68e05d29c189cb1fb06d8b4523a6f2e","tid":2089957,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200702/20947720/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947720%2F&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9T8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=ee74f966\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947720%2F&h=d46cc7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200702/20947720/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n收口抄家治國平天下 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200702/large/1593597180_74bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200702%2Flarge%2F1593597180_74bd.jpg&h=5d8e48cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六月三十日晚上十一點，「港區國安法」準時刊憲，着實讓我失望了一陣子。切勿誤會我是感慨「一國兩制」釘蓋，我沒有。失望的原因主要有二。<br />\n<br />\n一者，刊憲沒擇吉時，我擔<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n論語》也燒掉，以策安全。我剛剛已燒了。<br />\n<br />\n二者，刊憲即公開「國安法」，我也擔心影響國家安全。梁愛詩之前說「不公開條文是為免市民反對」，現在不一樣可以反對？抑或反對此法已經犯法了？如果真的不想市民反對，方法只有一個（是網友陳君提議的）：索性把「港區國安法」列為國家不能說的機密，堅決不公開，或像陳同佳的自首準則一樣，「有心情」才考慮公開，豈不更能體現黨的無上權威？<br />\n<br />\n考「港區國安法」原意，是藉着恐嚇香港「一小撮人」，消除黨的恐懼，理論上港人越害怕，黨越安全。老子說：「魚不可脫於淵，國之利器不可以示人。」「國安法」刊憲，大家就見到滿頭飛刀，還可左閃右避；「國安法」不刊憲，就成了六脈神劍的無形劍氣，疑心生暗鬼，那才是最可怕。Boris Johnson 揚言研究「國安法」有沒有違反「中英聯合聲明」，假若黨直接宣布「國安法」生效而不刊憲，那麼英國就無法研究，歐洲就不能觀察，美帝也不知制裁什麼了。<br />\n<br />\n既然立法過程大條道理不<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n全套《四書》都付之一炬，才有一點兒踏實。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"7b477155879c51111e11e2666a393d18ab88d252","tid":2089957,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}